{"id":1101,"name":"Letter from Lipsius, Justus to Clusius, Carolus, 1603-07-24","paralleltexts":{"Diplomatic":{"text":"<body>I[ustus] Lipsius Carolo Clusio S[alutem] D[icit].\n En tibi, mi Clusi, <ab id=\"9031377\"/>opusculum<ae id=\"9031377\"/> nostrum novitium, quod in languore hoc (qui etiamnunc detinet) dedimus, animi aliquam levem occupationem. Nihil agere non possumus, seria neque item possumus. Haec succedunt, sed cum notis etiam, opinor, nostri morbi. De pace sermo hic iterum erat, sed cui fidem apud me non nisi res dabit. Valere te, mi optime et amicissime vir, opto, saeculum totum. Lovanii, IX. Kal[lendas] Sextil[es], M.DCIII.\n  \n    [<i>Address</i>:] Cl[arissi]mo viro Carolo Clusio Leidam. Cum libro.\n    [<i>Manu Clusii</i>:] 1603 I[usti] Lipsii. Lovanii IX. K[a]l[endas] Sextiles. Accepi Leydae IX. K[a]l[endas] Septembr[es]. <ab id=\"9031378\"/>Respondi<ae id=\"9031378\"/> III. K[a]l[endas] eiusd[em].</body>","annotations":[{"text":"opusculum: <span><em>De Vesta et Vestalibus Syntagma </em>(Antwerp: J. Moretus, 1603)<em><br/></em></span>","n":9031377,"type":{"description":"Any annotation","name":"Uncategorized"}},{"text":"Respondi: Not preserved.","n":9031378,"type":{"description":"Any annotation","name":"Uncategorized"}}]}},"facsimiles":[{"thumbnail":"https://tomcat.tiler01.huygens.knaw.nl/adore-djatoka/resolver?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&svc_id=info:lanl-repo/svc/getRegion&svc_val_fmt=info:ofi/fmt:kev:mtx:jpeg2000&svc.format=image/jpeg&svc.level=0&rft_id=http://localhost:8080/jp2/clusius/893619_CLUY020-020-a.jp2","zoom":"https://tomcat.tiler01.huygens.knaw.nl/adore-huygens-viewer-2.0/viewer.html?rft_id=http://localhost:8080/jp2/clusius/893619_CLUY020-020-a.jp2"},{"thumbnail":"https://tomcat.tiler01.huygens.knaw.nl/adore-djatoka/resolver?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&svc_id=info:lanl-repo/svc/getRegion&svc_val_fmt=info:ofi/fmt:kev:mtx:jpeg2000&svc.format=image/jpeg&svc.level=0&rft_id=http://localhost:8080/jp2/clusius/893620_CLUY020-020-b.jp2","zoom":"https://tomcat.ti